_sText:
This was my 2nd real map I worked on in 2004 using Hammer because QuArK didn't have support for the Source engine. I had to learn how to use Hammer back then, so the map is a bit crude.

Unknown - Bomb Defuse

by Soctom	

Counter-Terrorists: Protect the abandoned
military base from a terrorist attack.

Terrorists: Blow up the abandoned military
base to release deadly nerve gas.

Map Notes: This map was supposed to be
released back in 2004 for a server with 64
player slots. I've redone a few things to make
the game play more fun, also the map only has
32 player spawns now. This map was made in a
week back in 2004 and fixed up in 2 days in 2007.
The map was never released in 2004 because no one
played on the guys 64 player server so he shut it down,
and I never released it until now.

(Press FIRE to continue)
